Package: babelmixr2
Type: Package
Title: Use nlmixr2 as a Front-End for Other Software
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Matthew","Fidler", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "matthew.fidler@gmail.com", comment=c(ORCID="0000-0001-8538-6691")),
           person("Bill", "Denney", email="wdenney@humanpredictions.com", role="aut", comment=c(ORCID="0000-0002-5759-428X")))
Description: Run other estimation and simulation software via the nlmixr2
  interface including NONMEM and Monolix. While not required, you can
  get/install the R 'lixoftConnectors' package in the 'Monolix' installation, as
  described at the following url
  <https://monolix.lixoft.com/monolix-api/lixoftconnectors_installation/>. When
  'lixoftConnectors' is available, R can 'Monolix' directly instead of using a
  command line.
